# C Programming Repository 🚀

Welcome to my C programming journey! This repository contains a curated collection of C programs I've written while learning and practicing the C language. It includes everything from basic syntax to advanced problem-solving.

## 🧠 What's Inside

- ✅ Basic Programs (Hello World, Input/Output, Math Operations)
- 🔁 Loops and Conditional Statements
- 🔣 Functions (With and Without Parameters)
- 🧩 Pattern Printing
- 🔢 Number Series and Special Numbers
- 🧮 Arrays and Strings (Coming Soon)
- 🧠 Recursion, Pointers, and Structures (Coming Soon)
- 🧪 Debugging & Output Prediction Exercises

> I’m constantly updating this repo as I progress through C programming.
